{"tid":208724,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"狐 妖 何 雁 詩 承 認 患 情 緒 病 賴 網 民 Cyberbully 佢 所 致 ！","createTime":"2017-04-19T17:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T05:58:02.000Z","uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7483851749de891084b6f9aeae7c2607f45c9c4","tid":208724,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:08:32.000Z","msg":"被爆成為「第三者」、介入鄭俊弘與未婚妻Beebs感情嘅何雁詩，最後更以勝利者身份，與鄭俊弘十指緊扣現身機場宣示戀情，又<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>承認患情緒病</strong>。</span><br />\n<br />\n何雁詩同鄭欣宜今日喺銅鑼灣出席ANNA SUI彩妝專櫃開幕，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">提到與鄭俊弘嘅戀情一波三折，何雁詩都話想放假休息下</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對於患上情緒病，何雁詩話唔想多講，只謂「呢個病一直都有」。至於被指第三者，心理壓力是否倍增？她稱：「邊個俾人話都會唔舒服，好彩身邊嘅朋友好錫我、好撐我，陳瀅keep住我Instagram、幫我刪留言，佢好保護我。」可是受網絡欺凌？何雁詩表示係其中一個原因。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/20/010811_e56e37cf274cf47528d3ab98177db201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F20%2F010811_e56e37cf274cf47528d3ab98177db201.jpg&h=d6441abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qC60Pub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqC60Pub.jpg&h=60096462&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21a4fd2a795abaa28efea54b1493327dde3a3f65","tid":208724,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"咪拎情緒病做盾牌啦"},{"pid":"1a0c526a064555a9e24f4a66bcd5d2f72ed4e3bc","tid":208724,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"618ae0810a95868576302b6a0984b2cec90aed79","tid":208724,"uid":25179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"個個都話自己有病 做公眾人物壓力自然會大 有人鐘意都有人唔鐘意 <br />\n好憎啲偽人個個話自己有病博同情<br />\n邊行都有壓力咖啦 你有病威啲咖？"},{"pid":"ab08ef6818171b774a7f479d4791eaa5ca5c420f","tid":208724,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"